snippet.title: Let's Build a Zoo: Dinosaur Island Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Let's Build a Zoo: Dinosaur Island now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1903410/Lets_Build_a_Zoo_Dinosaur_Island/

Join the official Discord: http://discord.gg/letsbuildazoo

Escape to a brand new DINOSAUR ISLAND and discover a world of prehistoric beasts. Start a brand new zoo complete with terrifying (and adorable!) creatures, brand new themed shops and a whole host of new decorations to give your guests the ultimate dinosaur experience!
